PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F358A1675716933
OL,6,FBut yet again ITV 1's scheduling of
OL,7,FNews at Ten is undermining what should
OL,8,Fbe one of the channel's flagships.
OL,10,FNews at Ten was brought back in 2008 `
OL,11,Finitially from Mondays to Thursdays but
OL,12,Fsoon afterwards the programme started
OL,13,Fto appear on Fridays too.
OL,15,FThe move was instigated by Michael
OL,16,FGrade who was well aware of the damage
OL,17,Fthe initial decision to axe News at Ten
OL,18,Fin 1999 had done.
OL,3,CAre we slowly drifting from News at Ten
OL,4,Cto News at When again?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,E]GArticle Published -- 29-Apr-22 2345
PN,35803
SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F358A1675716933
OL,6,FThe revival never regained the
OL,7,Faudiences of old ` and there is an
OL,8,Fargument that it isn't helpful to have
OL,9,Fthe news on both major channels
OL,10,Fsimultaneously ` but it was broadly
OL,11,Fwelcomed by journalists and others who
OL,12,Frealise the vital role high quality
OL,13,Fbroadcast journalism plays in a
OL,14,Fdemocratic society.
OL,16,FThe scheduling was never fixed and ITV
OL,17,Fappeared to toy with ditching the
OL,18,Fprogramme in 2017 when it experimented
OL,19,Fwith nightly chat shows at 10pm.
OL,3,CAre we slowly drifting from News at Ten
OL,4,Cto News at When again?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
