PN,35804
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F358A1675716933
OL,6,FBut in recent months there have been
OL,7,Fmore occasions when News at When has
OL,8,Freturned. There has scarcely been a
OL,9,Fweek for some time when the programme
OL,10,Fhas been shown at 10pm each night.
OL,12,FSometimes this has been because of
OL,13,Ffootball ` though it should be noted
OL,14,Fthat the BBC usually manages to get to
OL,15,Fthe news on time unless the game goes
OL,16,Fto extra time.
OL,18,FSometimes though this is because the
OL,19,F9pm programme is longer than usual. A
OL,20,Fdeliberate decision was taken to
OL,21,Fcommission or schedule a programme
OL,22,Fwhich wasn't made for a 60-minute slot.
OL,3,CAre we slowly drifting from News at Ten
OL,4,Cto News at When again?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
