OL,6,FThere would seem to be little
OL,7,Fcommercial advantage in the move as ITV
OL,8,F1 currently runs few ads between 10pm
OL,9,Fand 11pm. The last breaks during
OL,10,FMidsomer Murders were filled by
OL,11,Fpromotions.
OL,13,FYet it also meant excellent journalism
OL,14,F` including a powerful piece on an
OL,15,Fupsurge of serous Covid cases in China
OL,16,F` was seen by a relatively modest
OL,17,Faudience.
OL,19,FIt really is time for this scheduling
OL,20,Fshenanigans to end.
OL,3,CAre we slowly drifting from News at Ten
OL,4,Cto News at When again?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
