PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F358A1675716933
OL,6,FWould ITV 1 be better off anchoring the
OL,7,Fbulletin at 10.30pm? That way those who
OL,8,Fwanted to could easily watch the
OL,9,Fflagship bulletins of both main
OL,10,Fchannels?
OL,12,FMight it even be acceptable to move the
OL,13,Fprogramme to 11pm given that ITV now
OL,14,Fshows an hour of national news in the
OL,15,Fearly evening? (Even it is cut back to
OL,16,F30 minutes not infrequently.)
OL,3,CAre we slowly drifting from News at Ten
OL,4,Cto News at When again?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/8
