OL,6,FWhat might happen if ITV 1 gets
OL,7,Fpermission to run more ads in peak time
OL,8,Fwith a full 12 minutes allocated to the
OL,9,F10pm hour? If ITV cannot commit to
OL,10,Fgiving News at Ten a fixed berth, it is
OL,11,Fbetter to move it out of peak rather
OL,12,Fthen see it move like a ship in a
OL,13,Fstorm.
OL,3,CAre we slowly drifting from News at Ten
OL,4,Cto News at When again?
